title: Churchill Mountain
text: Churchill Mountain is a <a href="mountain">mountain</a> located in the <a href="Catskill%20Mountains">Catskill Mountains</a> of <a href="New%20York%20%28state%29">New York</a> east-southeast of <a href="Stamford%2C%20New%20York">Stamford</a>. <a href="Utsayantha%20Mountain">Utsayantha Mountain</a> is located northeast, <a href="Cowan%20Mountain">Cowan Mountain</a> is located southwest, and <a href="McGregor%20Mountain">McGregor Mountain</a> is located east of Churchill Mountain.
